title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Oh, Hello - meet American Wolf
description:
In Oh Hello!" meet American Wolf, who are a four-piece based out of Chicago, IL. Listen to the band explain how they create music, their past recording experiences and how far they have come together to experience the state-of-the-art studio session at Converse Rubber Tracks. 
For more on Converse Rubber Tracks: http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
